headline: Huntington Bancshares Incorporated Decreases Its Prime Rate To 7.5 Percent
summary: Huntington Bancshares Incorporated (Nasdaq: HBAN) announced that its prime rate is decreasing from 7.75 percent to 7.5 percent, effective December 19, 2024.
